### Health
GET http://localhost:5057/health

### List products
GET http://localhost:5057/api/products?page=1&pageSize=5

### Create product
POST http://localhost:5057/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Hat",
  "description": "A simple test product",
  "price": 10.5,
  "image": "https://picsum.photos/id/1062/800/800"
}

### Update product (replace {id})
PUT http://localhost:5057/api/products/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 12.0
}

### Get product
GET http://localhost:5057/api/products/{{id}}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:5057/api/products/{{id}}

